The paper proposes a methodology that combines Artificial Neural Network (ANN) and Auto-Regressive and Moving Average (ARMA) model to forecast hourly global radiation in Mediterranean area. This involves the use of machine learning techniques and time series analysis, which are commonly associated with sub-categories such as Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Systems and Control (cs.SD), and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
